dataset.description: Psychiatric facilities that are eligible for the Inpatient Psychiatric Facility Quality Reporting (IPFQR) program are required to meet all program requirements, otherwise their Medicare payments may be reduced. Follow-Up After Hospitalization for Mental Illness (FUH) measure data on this table are marked as not available. Results for this measure are provided on a separate table.
